    function "update_word_pattern from hangman.py

============================
=  Section C - q1  =
============================

update_word_pattern("hello", "_____", "h"): Check if works when pattern is blank
update_word_pattern("hello", "hell_", "h"): Check what happen if the letter is already been revealed
update_word_pattern("hello", "hell_", "o"): Ordinary case
update_word_pattern("hello", "h____", "d"): Check what happen if the letter is not in the word


